These two C files (myhdl.c, myhdl_table.c) are the Icarus Verilog VPI
bridge from the MyHDL project (https://www.myhdl.org/), vendored here so
the co-simulation tests build reliably regardless of where `pip install
myhdl` places its data files.

They are part of MyHDL and remain licensed under the GNU LGPL v2.1
(the license of MyHDL), NOT the MIT license of the rest of this
repository. Copyright (c) Jan Decaluwe and MyHDL contributors.

Source: myhdl/cosimulation/icarus/ in the MyHDL distribution.
Used unmodified, only for building the test-time VPI module.
